invalid type: string "3. Study Treatment and Administration\n3.1 Investigational Product\nCVS-221 is supplied as 50 mg oral film-coated tablets. Matching placebo tablets are identical in appearance,\ntaste, and packaging.\n3.2 Dosage and Administration\nParticipants randomised to active treatment will receive CVS-221 50 mg once daily, taken orally in the morning\nBody mass index (calculated)
